    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Keep Your Costume Under Wraps</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <byline class="print_byline">By Frank DeCaro</byline>
      <byline class="normalized_byline">Decaro, Frank</byline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Combine black-and-white skull print boxers with orange skeleton-print T-shirt from Old Navy for under-wraps Halloween costume; photo (Pulse column: Halloween Special) (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>For men who hate costumes but want to get in the Halloween spirit, Old Navy has created boxer shorts that are appropriately creepy. The best, $7.50, come in an understated black and white skull print that looks more Day of the Dead than trick-or-treat. Pair them with an orange skeleton-print long sleeve T-shirt, $14.50.</p>
      </block>
